<div class="formWrapper">
    <h1>
        Computer and Technical Skills <button type="button" class="btn btn-outline-primary btn-sm"
                                              data-bs-toggle="modal" data-bs-target="#ExperienceModal">
            ?
        </button>
    </h1>
    <button type="button" class="mb-2 btn btn-outline-primary btn-sm" data-bs-toggle="modal"
            data-bs-target="#modalExample">
        Example
    </button>
    <form  id="TechnicalSkillForm" class="needs-validation" novalidate>
        <input type="hidden" id="hdfLastSectionVisitedId" value="60" />
        <input type="hidden" id="hdfTechnicalSkillId" />
    <div class="row">
        <div class="col-md-4">
            <label>What computer programs in Microsoft are you proficient in?</label>
            <div class="mt-2">
                <div class="custom-checkbox custom-control">
                    <input type="checkbox"
                           id="Microsoft Word" name="Msword" class="custom-control-input"><label class="custom-control-label" for="Microsoft Word">Microsoft Word</label>
                </div>
                <div class="custom-checkbox custom-control">
                    <input type="checkbox"
                           id="Microsoft Excel" name="Msexcel" class="custom-control-input"><label class="custom-control-label" for="Microsoft Excel">Microsoft Excel</label>
                </div>
                <div class="custom-checkbox custom-control">
                    <input type="checkbox"
                           id="Microsoft Power Point" name="MspowerPoint" class="custom-control-input"><label class="custom-control-label" for="Microsoft Power Point">
                        Microsoft Power
                        Point
                    </label>
                </div>
                <div class="custom-checkbox custom-control">
                    <input type="checkbox"
                           id="Microsoft Outlook Express" name="Msoutlook" class="custom-control-input"><label class="custom-control-label" for="Microsoft Outlook Express">
                        Microsoft
                        Outlook Express
                    </label>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-4">
            <label>What computer programs in Macintosh are you proficient in?</label>
            <div class="mt-2">
                <div class="custom-checkbox custom-control">
                    <input type="checkbox"
                           id="Macintosh Pages" name="MacPages" class="custom-control-input"><label class="custom-control-label" for="Macintosh Pages">Macintosh Pages</label>
                </div>
                <div class="custom-checkbox custom-control">
                    <input type="checkbox"
                           id="Macintosh Numbers" name="MacNumbers" class="custom-control-input"><label class="custom-control-label" for="Macintosh Numbers">
                        Macintosh
                        Numbers
                    </label>
                </div>
                <div class="custom-checkbox custom-control">
                    <input type="checkbox"
                           id="Macintosh Keynote" name="MacKeynote" class="custom-control-input"><label class="custom-control-label" for="Macintosh Keynote">
                        Macintosh
                        Keynote
                    </label>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-4">
            <label>
                What other standard creative or word processing computer programs are you
                proficient in?
            </label>
            <div class="mt-2">
                <div class="custom-checkbox custom-control">
                    <input type="checkbox"
                           id="Adobe Acrobat" name="AdobeAcrobat" class="custom-control-input"><label class="custom-control-label" for="Adobe Acrobat">Adobe Acrobat</label>
                </div>
                <div class="custom-checkbox custom-control">
                    <input type="checkbox"
                           id="Adobe Publisher" name="AdobePublisher" class="custom-control-input"><label class="custom-control-label" for="Adobe Publisher">Adobe Publisher</label>
                </div>
                <div class="custom-checkbox custom-control">
                    <input type="checkbox"
                           id="Adobe Illustrator" name="AdobeIllustrator" class="custom-control-input"><label class="custom-control-label" for="Adobe Illustrator">
                        Adobe
                        Illustrator
                    </label>
                </div>
                <div class="custom-checkbox custom-control">
                    <input type="checkbox"
                           id="Adobe Photoshop" name="AdobePhotoshop" class="custom-control-input"><label class="custom-control-label" for="Adobe Photoshop">Adobe Photoshop</label>
                </div>
                <div class="custom-checkbox custom-control">
                    <input type="checkbox" id="Google Suite" name="GoogleSuite"
                           class="custom-control-input"><label class="custom-control-label"
                                                               for="Google Suite">Google Suite</label>
                </div>
                <div class="custom-checkbox custom-control">
                    <input type="checkbox" id="Google Docs" name="GoogleDocs"
                           class="custom-control-input"><label class="custom-control-label"
                                                               for="Google Docs">Google Docs</label>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="row">
        <div class="col">
            <div class="form-group mt-2">
                <label for="other" class="mb-2">
                    What other programs have you learned
                    in your education that would be applicable to the career you want to pursue?
                </label><input name="Other" id="otherSkill" type="text" class="form-control" value="">
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <hr>
    
        <div class="form-check">
            <label class="form-check-label">
                <input type="checkbox" id="ckbIsComplete" name="IsComplete"
                       class="form-check-input"> I am finished with this section
            </label>
        </div>
        <div class="formbtn-Wrapper">
            <button type="button" id="btnSaveAndContinue" class="btn btn-primary custombtn w-auto">
                Save and
                Continue
            </button>
        </div>
    </form>
</div>
<div class="modal fade" id="modalExample" tabindex="-1" aria-labelledby="exampleModalLabel" aria-hidden="true">
    <div class="modal-dialog">
        <div class="modal-content">
            <div class="modal-body">
                <h1><strong>Computer Skills</strong></h1>
                <p>Microsoft Word, Excel, PowerPoint, Google Docs, Tumblr, Foursquare</p>
                <h1>COMPUTER SKILLS</h1>
                <p>Macintosh Pages, Numbers, and Notes, Google Suite</p>
                <h1><strong>Technological Skills</strong></h1>
                <p>Microsoft Word, Excel, PowerPoint, C++, Javascript</p>
            </div>
            <div class="modal-footer">
                <button type="button" class="btn btn-secondary custombtn w-auto"
                        data-bs-dismiss="modal">
                    Close
                </button>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
<div class="modal fade" id="ExperienceModal" role="dialog" tabindex="-1">
    <div class="modal-dialog" role="document">
        <div class="modal-content">
            <div class="modal-body">
                <p>
                    Being able to take ‘red eye’ out of your friends’ pics in Photoshop doesn’t make it relevant to
                    the job – unless it’s a photography one- so think about that before you include it for certain
                    employers. Graphic arts/design/architecture candidates need to list ALL relevant programs for
                    the job. Ditto for CIS, engineering, or other technical fields. Evaluate what you include based
                    on the job description and the company.
                </p>
                <p>
                    And those of you who are in journalism and broadcasting have another whole set of programs to
                    make sure and include. Social media networking (Facebook® and Linked In® and blogging etc.)
                    could also be important to include depending on the position. Bottom line is if you would use
                    those skills/programs at the job, include them!
                </p>
            </div>
            <div class="modal-footer">
                <button type="button" class="btn btn-primary custombtn w-auto"
                        data-bs-dismiss="modal">
                    Close
                </button>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
@section Scripts{
    <script src="~/scripts/technicalskill/technicalskill.js"></script>
}